summary: Completed comprehensive testing of TopTube World Pro - YouTube channel tracking SaaS application. Backend API and frontend UI both functioning correctly with minor code quality issues identified.

design_issues.issue: React hydration warnings for HTML table nesting - span elements as children of tr/tbody elements
Chart width/height warnings but functionality not affected

passed_tests: All 15 backend API endpoints (100% success rate)
Homepage loads with stats (20 countries, 10 channels)
World map displays and navigation works
Global Top 100 leaderboard shows channels correctly
Countries page lists all countries with flags and top channels
Country detail pages show rankings and podium
Channel detail pages display stats and growth charts
Admin dashboard shows proper stats and controls
Admin search functionality works with YouTube API
Navigation between all pages (Home, Top 100, Countries, Trending, Admin)
success_percentage: Backend: 100% (15/15 tests passed), Frontend: 95% (minor console warnings only)
